query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.tenantId,
  t.name as cliente,
  wl.code as endereco,
  p.sku,
  i.quantity
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE wl.code IN ('Z01-01-01', 'Z01-01-02', 'Z01-01-03', 'Z01-01-04')
ORDER BY wl.code;
